'''尼卡·格瓦拉米亞'''（{{lang-ka|ნიკოლოზ [ნიკა] გვარამია}}；{{bd|1976年|6月29日}}），是一位[[喬治亞|喬治亞]]政治家。他曾經擔任喬治亞司法部長和喬治亞教育與科學部長。在參政之前他曾經是一名[[律師|律師]]<ref name=Min>{{cite web |url=http://justice.gov.ge/index.php?sec_id=187&lang_id=ENG |title=Ministry of Justice of Georgia. Nika Gvaramia - 2008/01/31 - 2008/10/27 |accessdate=2011-04-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110817000237/http://www.justice.gov.ge/index.php?sec_id=187&lang_id=ENG |archivedate=2011-08-17 }}</ref>。2008年1月31日，他被任命為司法部長<ref name=Min/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=17023 |title=Cabinet Wins Confidence Vote |publisher=Civil Georgia |date=2008-01-31 |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2012-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918012444/http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=17023 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=16984 |title=New Cabinet Named |publisher=Civil Georgia |date=2008-01-24 |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2012-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918012449/http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=16984 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年10月27日，他改任教育與科學部長。2009年12月7日，他辭去教育與科學部長職務前往外國留學<ref>{{cite news |url=http://georgiamediacentre.com/content/carousel_starts_its_turn_education_minister_quits |title=The carousel starts its turn as education minister quits |publisher=Georgian International Media Centre |date=2009-12-07 |accessdate=2011-04-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.government.gov.ge/index.php?lang_id=ENG&sec_id=157&info_id=29959 |title=Staff Changes in the Government |accessdate=2011-04-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928081955/http://www.government.gov.ge/index.php?lang_id=ENG&sec_id=157&info_id=29959 |archivedate=2011-09-28 }}</ref>。2012年12月19日，喬治亞財政部的調查部門宣布格瓦拉米亞因涉嫌腐敗被捕<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=25564 |title=civil.ge - Ex-minister arrested |accessdate=2015-12-14 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222081459/http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=25564 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

